00:14:19,575 --> 00:14:24,958
as good outcome as success. It's when you don't know which one it is that makes it really difficult.

267
00:14:25,918 --> 00:14:31,120
But the team needs to have that permission to fail so they can actually take some bold steps.

268
00:14:32,481 --> 00:14:39,284
So, the core limits to this test is, can the team build it? And then hand the controller over to

