00:17:40,894 --> 00:17:44,616
especially since we didn't know if there was a dare there with this sort of experience.

309
00:17:45,757 --> 00:17:50,760
And we were lucky. We actually found that magic kind of early. It was about in that

310
00:17:52,120 --> 00:17:58,184
seven to nine month type of window that we were able to unlock what was special about it.

311
00:17:59,185 --> 00:18:03,607
With Knockout City, we had this core idea of throwing and catching a ball.

312
00:18:04,676 --> 00:18:10,238
And every three months or so, we thought we had this core figured out. We put it in the hands

