00:18:10,278 --> 00:18:15,940
of trusted peers and it failed. It wasn't fun. There were problems with it. But the team kept

314
00:18:16,080 --> 00:18:22,243
at it. And it actually took 18 months to really nail that core experience that felt great in

315
00:18:22,283 --> 00:18:28,705
people's hands. Sometimes it's really hard to know when you should cut bait on an idea and move on

316
00:18:28,805 --> 00:18:31,967
or keep going. And at the end of the day, you got to trust the team.

